                <head>The Old Game</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>SS is complaining that the VA Democratic party is sowing the seeds of
                    sectionalism for the 1860 election by claiming to be the true protector of the
                    South.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>The Comet</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>Last Saturday, the day fixed for the destruction of the world by a comet,
                    to the great relief of many nervous people, passed off quietly and without
                    special incident.</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Despite predictions to the contrary, the world was not destroyed by a comet
                    on 6/13.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Another Split</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Southern members of the General Assembly of the New School Presbyterian
                    Church have decided to secede and form a new church, one that will not discuss
                    slavery. Should not affect Virginia churches, since most of them are Old
                School.</summary>
            </div>
            <pageNote>Lots of news about a lynching in Rockingham Co.</pageNote>
        </page>
